A student from Ntuzuma in KZN has proven it's never too late to turn your life around. eNCA’s Lethiwe Mdluli has more.#DStv403 #eNCA  KWAZULU-NATAL - A student from Ntuzuma in KZN has proven it's never too late to turn your life around. Emmanuel Hare (24) obtained five distinctions in Matric last year. He beat the odds after turning to drugs and dropping out of school. But a decision to turn his life around is yielding big rewards. eNCA’a Lethiwe Mdluli has more in the video above.